g src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/391410/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/391410/page/1</a><br />\nLIHKG香港女神總會盃第一圈抽籤結果<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/390687\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/390687</a><br />\nLIHKG環球女神冠軍盃分組賽抽籤結果"},{"pid":"fe0e03ccd2e274c1cc0790a28a70b4ecc614262f","tid":411303,"uid":129039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T16:50:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>票已投<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d822b5a592a4d16aefcef5d7286ca19fb8a66bb","tid":411303,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T16:54:22.000Z","msg":"0:52 即時綜述<br />\n賴慰玲v周慧敏 主隊開局唔錯,果然岩岩嫁人係旺啲既<br />\n王敏奕v湯洛雯 榜首大戰暫時不相上下<br />\n胡琳v何雁詩 呢場都係差唔多喎<br />\n陳寶珊v駱文捷 客隊表現較好<br />\n陳婉婷v蘇麗珊 客隊表現較好<br />\n勞嘉怡v歐鎧淳 主隊稍稍佔先<br />\n蔡思貝v林映蔚 主隊開局幾猛喎<br />\n陳潔玲v黃德藍 前列女神對住弱女表現正常<br />\n朱智賢v菊梓喬 主隊優勢明顯"},{"pid":"44743ee2622a0889696b23b2c60d9180287126c3","tid":411303,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T16:55:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/411254\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/411254</a><br />\n甲組都開左,係咪出現搵唔到個post呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4979d18dafe77b38d351f6fe88187329a3df590","tid":411303,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T17:25:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7b884a6ed0ce630d6c1383660730b95f24bf9f3","tid":411303,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T17:39:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongu